<includeonly><div class="citation"><blockquote>{{{text}}}<small>{{{source}}}</small></blockquote></div></includeonly>
<noinclude>[[Category:Official Templates]]
Usage:

This template has to be used only for quotes in the homepage of a department. For quotes inside a chapter use the template quote.

<code><nowiki>{{Citation|text=This is a citation|source=Mr. Author}}</nowiki></code>

Result:
{{Citation|text=This is a citation|source=Mr. Author}}
</noinclude>
